videos.headline: Ferguson tosses short TD pass for Memphis
videos.description: Riley Ferguson connects with Anthony Miller on a 5-yard touchdown pass as the Tigers take a 7-3 lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Ferguson tosses short TD pass for Memphis) 2017/10/14 ESHEET

videos.headline: Memphis INT leads to red zone opportunity
videos.description: Austin Hall cuts off the pass from Zach Abey and returns it to the Navy 12-yard line for great field position.

videos.headline: Tigers capitalize on turnover with TD
videos.description: Riley Ferguson finds Darrell Henderson streaking on the sideline for the 12-yard touchdown grab to put Memphis up.

videos.headline: Navy scores on QB keeper
videos.description: Zach Abey finds a seam on the right side and slips through for the 8-yard score.

videos.headline: Midshipmen stay close with TD and 2 pt. conversion
videos.description: Zach Abey pounds in a 1-yard touchdown and then  Darryl Bonner makes it a 3-point game with the two-point conversion.

videos.headline: Hall with 2nd INT to clinch the W
videos.description: Austin Hall leaps and comes down with the big interception that seals the victory over Navy.
